\c 30
\s Abantu bagcina iphasika
\p
\v 1 UHezekhiya wasethumela kuIsrayeli wonke loJuda, wasebhalela loEfrayimi loManase izincwadi, ukuthi beze endlini yeN\nd kosi\nd* eJerusalema ukwenzela iN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu kaIsrayeli iphasika.
\v 2 Ngoba inkosi yelulekana lezikhulu zayo lebandla lonke eJerusalema ukwenza iphasika ngenyanga yesibili\x + 30.13,15. Nani 9.10,11.\x*.
\v 3 Ngoba babengelakukwenza ngalesosikhathi\x + 29.17. Eks. 12.6,18.\x* ngoba abapristi babengazingcwelisanga ngokweneleyo, labantu babengabuthananga eJerusalema\x + 29.34. 30.24.\x*.
\v 4 Lodaba lwaluqondile emehlweni enkosi lemehlweni ebandla lonke.
\v 5 Basebemisa ilizwi ukwedlulisela isimemezelo kuIsrayeli wonke\x + Ezra 1.1.\x* kusukela eBherishebha kusiya koDani\x + 2 Sam. 3.10.\x*, ukuthi bazekwenzela iN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu kaIsrayeli iphasika eJerusalema; ngoba okwesikhathi eside babengenzanga njengokubhaliweyo.
\v 6 Ngakho izigijimi zahamba kuIsrayeli wonke loJuda zilezincwadi ezivela esandleni senkosi leziphathamandla zayo, langokomlayo wenkosi\x + 30.10. Esta 3.13,15. 8.10,14. Jobe 9.25. Jer. 51.31.\x* zisithi: Bantwana bakoIsrayeli, buyelani eN\nd kosi\nd*ni, uNkulunkulu kaAbrahama, uIsaka, loIsrayeli\x + 30.9. Jer. 4.1. Jow. 2.12,13.\x*, njalo izabuyela kwabaphunyukileyo abasele kini esandleni samakhosi eAsiriya\x + 2 Kho. 15.19,29.\x*.
\v 7 Njalo lingabi njengaboyihlo lanjengabafowenu ababephambuka eN\nd kosi\nd*ni uNkulunkulu waboyise\x + Hez. 20.18.\x*, yaze yabanikela ekuchithweni njengoba libona\x + 29.8. 2 Kho. 22.19.\x*.
\v 8 Khathesi lingaqinisi intamo yenu njengaboyihlo; zinikeleni\f + \fk zinikeleni \fl Heb. \fq nika isandla.\f* eN\nd kosi\nd*ni, lingene endlini yayo engcwele eyingcwelise kuze kube nininini\x + Dute. 9.6. Eks. 32.9.\x*, likhonze iN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wenu, ukuze ukuvutha kolaka lwayo kubuyele emuva kusuke kini\x + 29.10.\x*.
\v 9 Ngoba ekubuyeleni kwenu eN\nd kosi\nd*ni, abafowenu labantwana benu \add bazathola\add* izihawu phambi kwababathumbileyo, ukuze babuye kulelilizwe\x + Hlab. 106.46.\x*. Ngoba iN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wenu ilomusa\x + Eks. 34.6. Eks. 22.27.\x* lesihawu\x + Dute. 4.31.\x*, kayiyikuphendula ubuso busuke kini uba libuyela kuyo\x + 1 Sam. 7.3.\x*.
\v 10 Ngokunjalo izigijimi zedlula zisuka emzini zisiya emzini elizweni\x + 30.10. Esta 3.13,15. 8.10,14. Jobe 9.25. Jer. 51.31.\x* lakoEfrayimi lelakoManase kuze kube koZebuluni\x + 30.1.\x*; kodwa bazihleka baziklolodela\x + 36.16.\x*.
\v 11 Kube kanti abanye bakoAsheri labakoManase labakoZebuluni bazithoba, beza eJerusalema\x + 30.18,21,25. 11.16.\x*.
\v 12 LakoJuda isandla sikaNkulunkulu sasikhona ukubanika inhliziyonye ukwenza umlayo wenkosi leziphathamandla ngelizwi likaJehova\x + 29.15.\x*.
\p
\v 13 Kwasekubuthana eJerusalema abantu abanengi ukwenza umkhosi wesinkwa esingelamvubelo ngenyanga yesibili, ibandla elikhulu kakhulu\x + 30.2.\x*.
\v 14 Basebesukuma basusa amalathi ayeseJerusalema, lawo wonke amalathi okutshisela impepha bawasusa\x + 28.24. 2 Kho. 18.4.\x*, bawaphosela esihotsheni iKidroni\x + 15.16. 2 Kho. 23.6. 2 Sam. 15.23.\x*.
\v 15 Basebehlaba iphasika ngolwetshumi lane lwenyanga yesibili\x + 30.2.\x*; abapristi lamaLevi basebeyangeka\x + 29.34.\x*, bazingcwelisa, baletha iminikelo yokutshiswa endlini yeN\nd kosi\x + Ezra 6.20.\x*\nd*.
\v 16 Basebesima endaweni yabo ejwayelekileyo njengendlela yabo ngokomlayo kaMozisi umuntu kaNkulunkulu\x + Dute. 33.1.\x*; abapristi bafafaza igazi elalivela esandleni samaLevi.
\v 17 Ngoba babebanengi ebandleni ababengazingcwelisanga; ngakho amaLevi ayephezu kokuhlatshwa kwamaphasika kwalowo lalowo owayengahlambulukanga uku\add ba\add*ngcwelisela iN\nd kosi\nd*.
\v 18 Ngoba ixuku labantu, abanengi bakoEfrayimi, loManase, uIsakari, loZebuluni babengazihlambululanga\x + 30.11,25.\x*, kube kanti badla iphasika kungenjengokubhaliweyo. Kodwa uHezekhiya wabakhulekela wathi: IN\nd kosi\nd* elungileyo kayimenzele inhlawulo yokuthula\x + 30.5. Eks. 12.43.\x*,
\v 19 wonke olungise inhliziyo yakhe ukudinga uNkulunkulu, iN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu waboyise, lanxa kungenjengokuhlanjululwa kwendawo engcwele\x + 19.3.\x*.
\v 20 IN\nd kosi\nd* yasimuzwa uHezekhiya, yabelapha abantu.
\p
\v 21 Abantwana bakoIsrayeli abatholakala eJerusalema basebesenza umkhosi wesinkwa esingelamvubelo insuku eziyisikhombisa ngentokozo enkulu; lamaLevi labapristi bayidumisa iN\nd kosi\nd* insuku ngensuku, ngezinto zokuhlabelela ngamandla eN\nd kosi\nd*ni\x + Ezra 6.22.\x*.
\v 22 UHezekhiya wasekhuluma ngomusa kumaLevi wonke ayelokuqedisisa elwazini oluhle lweN\nd kosi\nd*. Badla-ke \add oko\add*mkhosi omisiweyo insuku eziyisikhombisa benikela iminikelo yokuthula\x + 35.3.\x*, beyidumisa iN\nd kosi\nd*, uNkulunkulu waboyise\x + Levi 5.5.\x*.
\v 23 Ibandla lonke laselicebisana ukwenza ezinye insuku eziyisikhombisa; benza ezinye insuku eziyisikhombisa ngentokozo\x + 1 Kho. 8.65.\x*.
\v 24 Ngoba uHezekhiya inkosi yakoJuda wanika ibandla amajongosi azinkulungwane lezimvu eziyizinkulungwane eziyisikhombisa, leziphathamandla zanika ibandla amajongosi azinkulungwane lezimvu ezizinkulungwane ezilitshumi; labapristi bazingcwelisa ngobunengi\x + 30.3. 29.34.\x*.
\v 25 Ibandla lonke lakoJuda, labapristi lamaLevi, lebandla lonke elivela koIsrayeli, labezizweni ababevela elizweni lakoIsrayeli, lababehlala koJuda, basebethokoza\x + 30.11,18.\x*.
\v 26 Kwasekusiba khona intokozo enkulu eJerusalema, ngoba kusukela ensukwini zikaSolomoni indodana kaDavida inkosi yakoIsrayeli kakuzanga kube khona okunjalo eJerusalema\x + 7.9,10.\x*.
\p
\v 27 Basebesukuma abapristi lamaLevi\x + 23.18.\x*, babusisa abantu\x + Nani 6.23-27.\x*; ilizwi labo laselizwakala, lomkhuleko wabo wafika endaweni yakhe yokuhlala engcwele emazulwini.